<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Intranet - Services</title>
    
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">

    <style>
        /* --- 1. CSS GLOBAL --- */
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; }
        body { display: flex; background-color: #f4f6f8; min-height: 100vh; }
        
        /* Sidebar */
        .sidebar { width: 260px; background-color: #EAEAEA; display: flex; flex-direction: column; padding: 25px 0; height: 100vh; position: fixed; left: 0; top: 0; border-right: 1px solid #d1d1d1; }
        .logo { text-align: center; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 800; color: #000; margin-bottom: 40px; letter-spacing: 1px; }
        .menu-items { list-style: none; flex-grow: 1; }
        
        /* Alignement du menu */
        .menu-items a { display: flex; justify-content: flex-start; gap: 15px; align-items: center; padding: 12px 30px; text-decoration: none; color: #333; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 500; transition: all 0.3s ease; }
        .menu-items a:hover { background-color: #d6d6d6; color: #000; }
        .menu-items li.active a { background-color: #d1d1d1; font-weight: 700; border-left: 4px solid #333; }
        
        .logout-item { margin-top: auto; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        
        /* Contenu Principal */
        .main-content { margin-left: 260px; padding: 50px; width: 100%; }

        /* --- 2. CSS GRILLE SERVICES --- */
        .grid-container {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 25px;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        .service-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
            cursor: pointer;
            border-bottom: 3px solid transparent;
            display: block; 
            text-decoration: none; 
            color: inherit;
        }

        .service-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-7px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            border-bottom: 3px solid #333;
        }

        .service-card i {
            font-size: 45px;
            color: #444;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .service-card h4 {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #222;
        }

        .service-card p {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

   <nav class="sidebar">
        <div class="logo">ENTREPRISE</div>
        <ul class="menu-items">
            <li><a href="/employe-dashboard"><i class="fas fa-home"></i> Tableau de bord</a></li>
            <li class="active"><a href="/services"><i class="fas fa-concierge-bell"></i> Mes Services</a></li>
            <li><a href="/documents"><i class="fas fa-file-alt"></i> Documents</a></li>
            <li><a href="/departements"><i class="fas fa-building"></i> Départements</a></li>
            <li><a href="/applications"><i class="fas fa-laptop-code"></i> Applications</a></li>
            <li><a href="/apropos"><i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> À propos</a></li>
            
            <li class="logout-item">
                <a href="/logout" style="color: #c0392b;">
                    <i class="fas fa-sign-out-alt"></i> Déconnexion
                </a>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </nav>

    <main class="main-content">
        <h1>Catalogue des Services</h1>
        <p style="color: #666; margin-top: 10px;">Sélectionnez un service pour faire une demande ou obtenir de l'aide.</p>

        <div class="grid-container">
            
            <a href="/services/support" class="service-card">
                <i class="fas fa-laptop-medical" style="color: #2980b9;"></i>
                <h4>Support Informatique</h4>
                <p>Problème matériel, logiciel ou accès réseau ? Ouvrez un ticket ici.</p>
            </a>

            <a href="/services/rh" class="service-card">
                <i class="fas fa-user-clock" style="color: #8e44ad;"></i>
                <h4>Ressources Humaines</h4>
                <p>Gestion des congés, fiches de paie et arrêts maladie.</p>
            </a>

            <a href="/services/salles" class="service-card">
                <i class="fas fa-calendar-check" style="color: #27ae60;"></i>
                <h4>Réservation de Salles</h4>
                <p>Réservez une salle de réunion ou de conférence.</p>
            </a>

            <a href="/services/auto" class="service-card">
                <i class="fas fa-car-side" style="color: #c0392b;"></i>
                <h4>Flotte Automobile</h4>
                <p>Réservation de véhicules de service et gestion du carburant.</p>
            </a>

            <a href="/services/maintenance" class="service-card">
                <i class="fas fa-tools" style="color: #7f8c8d;"></i>
                <h4>Services Généraux</h4>
                <p>Réparations, climatisation, nettoyage et maintenance.</p>
            </a>

            <a href="/services/restauration" class="service-card">
                <i class="fas fa-utensils" style="color: #e67e22;"></i>
                <h4>Restauration</h4>
                <p>Menu de la cantine et rechargement de badge.</p>
            </a>

        </div>
    </main>

</body>
</html>